show.description: When skilled doctor Meher signs a secret contract to care for businessman Aarav Bajaj’s ailing mother, she never expects it to bind her into a fake marriage—and a web of hidden truths. As loyalties are tested and hearts unexpectedly connect, Meher and Aarav must confront love, lies, and second chances that change their lives forever. Watch Now!
